:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::

Title................: Hardstyle - The 50 Best
Artist...............: Various
Year.................: 2009
Genre................: Hardstyle
Duration.............: 3h 51m
Number of Songs......: 50
Audio Format.........: MP3
Bitrate..............: VBR to 320 (Various)

:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::

So basically, the track number in the id tags shows the top placement. This means, for example, that I find Her Voice by Builder to be the number one track, Da Bomba by Da Tweekaz the second best, et cetera. Of course, this is all my opinion and around the 10-40 mark it's kinda unclear because I'm lazy and could be arsed to sort them detailed.

All tracks have sexy tags. They all have artist and track title mp3 tags.

I also wanted to avoid to upload too much of the mainstream songs, that's why Project One -  The Art Of Creation and 2 Best Enemies - Phases among with other tracks that's in every mix in existance since 2008 aren't included, mkay?

Oh yeah this is mostly nu-style, I guess... Teehee.

Basically, I took the best versions of the tracks possible I had. This means 320kbps over VBRkbps and 192kbps if possible. I also tried taking the full versions of the tracks.
Anyways, enough with the formalities, enjoy your hardstyle and seed well... I mean, it's just music, have fun!

fratey
